               <msContents>
                  <summary>Cycle of Kings, እውዳ፡ ነገሥት፡, incomplete at the end, accompanied by sixteen charts based on the standard sixteen cycles.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="28v" facs="001">Fols 1r–28v</locus>
                     <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1171Awdana">ʿAwda nagaśt</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">፩ ሶበ፡ ተሐውር፡ ፍኖተ፡ ትረክብ፡ ሠናየ። ፪ እስመትረክብ፡ መኰንን፡ ይትቀበለከ። ፫ ዘእድሜ ነዊኅ፡ መዋዕሊከ።</incipit>
                     <note>incomplete at the end, accompanied by sixteen charts based on the ‎standard sixteen cycles‎</note>
                  </msItem>
              </msContents>
